Class LinkedQueue<E>

public class LinkedQueue<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

A LinkedQueue<E> is a queue of references to E objects.

Limitations:
Beyond Int.MAX_VALUE items, size is wrong.
